22
00:00:59.624 --> 00:01:01.235
You gotta leave!

23
00:01:01.278 --> 00:01:03.063
Everybody's gotta get out.

24
00:01:03.106 --> 00:01:06.631
Wake up! Wake up!
Everybody's gotta get out.

25
00:01:06.675 --> 00:01:08.633
You gotta leave.

26
00:01:08.677 --> 00:01:10.635
Can you hear me?
Everybody out!

27
00:01:10.679 --> 00:01:13.334
What's going on?
It's carbon monoxide.

28
00:01:13.377 --> 00:01:15.292
Fire department's on the way.
but you gotta get outside.

29
00:01:15.336 --> 00:01:16.685
Take the stairs.

30
00:01:16.728 --> 00:01:18.513
Come on. everyone. let's go!

31
00:01:18.556 --> 00:01:20.732
Everybody get out!
Carbon monoxide leak.

32
00:01:20.776 --> 00:01:23.431
Everybody out.
We gotta get out now!

33
00:01:23.474 --> 00:01:25.128
Carbon monoxide leak!
Everybody out!

34
00:01:25.172 --> 00:01:27.130
Everybody out!
We got a leak.

35
00:01:27.174 --> 00:01:28.740
Come on. man. you gotta
get out of here. boy.

36
